VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\bUNION\s+SELECT\s+.*\$.*
WHEN EXPR MISSING:(SqlParameter|AddWithValue|Parameters\.Add|Parameters\.AddWithValue)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects UNION queries that incorporate user input, which could allow SQL injection if not parameterized securely.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for SQL Query: UNION Queries with User Input.
